{"tid":694560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭通過無限期暫停港協暨奧委會會籍　空手道總會稱將上訴","createTime":"2018-06-08T12:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T15:32:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ee164d6df2f93c63f8469680afac784607f60d","tid":694560,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"港協暨奧委會召開會員大會，以55票中51票贊成，通過無限期暫停香港空手道總會的會籍。<br />\n<br />\n香港空手道總會主席余鏡秋對結果表示非常失望，並指已準備文件，對港協暨奧委會會章提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港空手道總會早前被指選拔港隊選手不公及行政失當，其最終改善方案早前未獲港協暨奧委會接受。港協暨奧委會早前已決定，今日召開會員大會，重新啟動3月時對空總提出的「無限期暫停空總會籍」議案。"},{"pid":"e29b9a8c21c62933b27f55852e83cd5545845dd0","tid":694560,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180608/s00001/1528456466623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180608%2Fs00001%2F1528456466623&d=TP16uof%2BsUC64KvAjN0iLL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=69765171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180608%2Fs00001%2F1528456466623&h=ffd49d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180608/s00001/1528456466623</a>"},{"pid":"5d2684818d67ecf7130e4839f98a381a014a67c4","tid":694560,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12bda88100621f8f266152329092b98f41ea9a40","tid":694560,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/233238_0337d8855094d1a45d3f0f2241c57a86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F233238_0337d8855094d1a45d3f0f2241c57a86.jpg&h=f39ad173&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}